metadata.name: thermonuclear dream
metadata.description:
the photo itself was made a couple years ago with my friends when i was experimenting with different light effects.

i decided to revisit the files a couple months back to do something in my current style and it just wasnâ€™t working out because i was constantly under stress because of work, personal life and health so i left it unfinished.

now when i finally achieved the freedom i was so desiring all these years of having the ability to create without worrying too much, without consequences of digging too much in my own head i created this and it feels like a breath of fresh air.
